    "name": "Duolingo: Hide the Hint",
    "description": "Hide text hints from Duolingo, only to display them after a delay.  This allows you to try to translate by first by hearing then by reading.",
    "additionalInfo": "V 0.3 - Fixed the \"hiding native hints\" problem.  (nth-child/button)\r\n\r\nV 0.2 - Hint will show when the mouse hovers over the hint.\r\n\r\nV 0.1 - Unfortunately, also hides your native language as well.  If duolingo changes their html structure, I might be able to eliminate that.",
